ural ingredients that you simply rub under your arms and lasts much longer than the aerosol deodorant. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/plastic-free-deodorant\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get your new deodorant here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130301\/plastic-free-deodorant-bar.jpg\" alt=\"plastic free deodorant bar\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"plastic free deodorant bar\" class=\"wp-image-17472 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130301\/plastic-free-deodorant-bar.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130301\/plastic-free-deodorant-bar-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130301\/plastic-free-deodorant-bar-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130301\/plastic-free-deodorant-bar-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130301\/plastic-free-deodorant-bar-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130301\/plastic-free-deodorant-bar-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-c