sable for up to 10 years! It might feel like a small investment, while 10 years of tampons and sanitary pads will cost you a lot more.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/plastic-free-mooncup\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get a menstrual cup<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130311\/easy-tips-travel-plastic-free.jpg\" alt=\"easy tips travel plastic free\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"327\" alt=\"easy tips travel plastic free\" class=\"wp-image-17462 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130311\/easy-tips-travel-plastic-free.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130311\/easy-tips-travel-plastic-free-300x218.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130311\/easy-tips-travel-plastic-free-600x437.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130311\/easy-tips-travel-plastic-free-450x327.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130311\/easy-tips-travel-plastic-free-800x582.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130311\/easy-tips-trave