 Bring your own soap block, shampoo, and tooth tabs so there are zero reasons to use hotel toiletries. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/plastic-free-soap\/\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Get your soap block here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130258\/zero-waste-soap-bar.jpg\" alt=\"travel plastic free soap\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"308\" alt=\"travel plastic free soap\" class=\"wp-image-17473 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130258\/zero-waste-soap-bar.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130258\/zero-waste-soap-bar-300x205.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130258\/zero-waste-soap-bar-600x410.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130258\/zero-waste-soap-bar-450x308.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130258\/zero-waste-soap-bar-800x547.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130258\/zero-waste-soap-bar-1080x738.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130258\/zero-waste-soap-bar-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/