iv><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip: <\/strong>Research for an environmentally friendly supermarket near you, as more supermarkets, are using zero-waste dispensing systems. Check out &#x2018;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Zero Waste Bali (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/zerowastebali.com\" target=\"_blank\">Zero Waste Bali<\/a>&#x2019; for inspiration!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"content_hint\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>10. <strong>Say &#x2018;No&#x2019; to plastic straws<\/strong> and <strong>utensils<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When traveling, the &#x2018;grab and go&#x2019; food comes with an environmental price- plastic utensils. Instead, always carry your tools with you and invest in a reusable <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/plastic-free-straws\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">stainless steel straw<\/a>, coffee mug, and <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"cutlery (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/plastic-free-cutlery\/\" target=\"_blank\">cutlery<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130254\/plastic-free-reusable-straws-575x810.jpg\" alt=\"travel plastic free straws\"><\/noscript><img width=\"240\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel plastic free straws\" class=\"wp-image-17474 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130254\/plastic-free-reusable-straws-575x810.jpg 575w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130254\/plastic-free-reusable-straws-300x423.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\