#x2013; 8 million tonnes of plastic ends up in the ocean every year in which fish eat and eventually ending up in the human body who eat the fish.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip block-link--long\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Top tip for travelers:<\/strong> Travelling in a country where the water isn&#x2019;t safe to drink? Instead of having to buy plastic water bottles from the supermarket, buy the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/plastic-free-lifestraw\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Life Straw<\/a> water purifying bottle.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130215\/coral-reef-safe-sunscreen-reduce-plastic.jpg\" alt=\"coral reef safe sunscreen reduce plastic\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"316\" alt=\"coral reef safe sunscreen reduce plastic\" class=\"wp-image-17542 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130215\/coral-reef-safe-sunscreen-reduce-plastic.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130215\/coral-reef-safe-sunscreen-reduce-plastic-300x211.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130215\/coral-reef-safe-sunscreen-reduce-plastic-600x421.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130215\/coral-re