strong>.<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Every 6 hours, 1 million plastic cups are used on US domestic flights alone! <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/how-to-plan-trip\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Plan for your trip<\/a> when traveling, by bringing&#xA0;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/plastic-free-bottle\/\">a reusable water bottle<\/a>. Airports typically have refill points before boarding, and most airlines will fill your water bottle for you on the flight if their water supply allows it. Sadly, airlines are still not obligated to provide you with free water, though, so make sure to double-check their policy before you fly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130240\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle.jpg\" alt=\"travel plastic free bottle\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"travel plastic free bottle\" class=\"wp-image-17478 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130240\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130240\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130240\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130240\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130240\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130240\/plastic-free-reusable-water-bottle-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\